    'NordLynx (NordVPN\'s WireGuard implementation) delivers consistently fast speeds. On a 1Gbps base connection, you\'ll rarely see more than 10-15% speed loss on nearby servers. Cross-continent connections suffer more, but that\'s physics, not NordVPN\'s fault.',
