    'R.O.B.E.R.T. is genuinely useful — it\'s a server-side DNS blocklist you configure per account. Block social media, gambling, fake news, or custom domains. This works across all your devices without browser extensions.',
    'Static IPs are available in the US, Canada, UK, Netherlands, Germany, France, Romania, Switzerland, and Turkey. Useful if you need a consistent IP address for a specific service.',
