    'ProtonVPN Free is the clear recommendation. Unlimited data, no ads, no data selling. The funding model (paid plans subsidize free users) is sustainable and transparent. The limitation is server access: only 3 countries (US, Netherlands, Japan) and speeds are throttled during peak hours. For basic privacy on public WiFi or occasional browsing, it works perfectly.',
    'Windscribe Free gives more server locations (11 countries) but caps data at 10-15GB per month. Enough for daily browsing but not for streaming HD video. The R.O.B.E.R.T. ad blocker works on the free tier, which is a genuine differentiator.',
