    'If 10GB/month is enough for your needs, Windscribe Free is solid. If you need unlimited data, ProtonVPN Free. If you need 50+ server locations and full streaming access, a paid VPN like <a href="/guides/surfshark-review-2026" class="text-emerald-400 hover:underline">Surfshark at $2.19/month</a> is the most affordable paid option.',
